column35:
The innovative and incomparable Original Mercedes-Benz Eau de Toilette is the perfect balance of freshness and sensuality, whose elegance and distinction lies in the marriage of seductive woody notes and magnificent fresh florals. A vibrant, original composition, woody, floral and fresh, reinterpreting and reinforcing the luxurious world of Mercedes-Benz.

Design- The design for the bottle embodies the values that define Mercedes-Benz: perceivable quality, passionate innovation, refined sportiness and distinctive style. The Mercedes-Benz emblem, the three-pointed star, is the symbol that expresses these brand values. Engraved in the base of the bottle and embossed into the cap, it lends the bottle design an unmistakably modern feel. 

Olfactive Family- Woody floral

Top Note -Bergamot, Violet leaves

Heart Note -Violet flower, Bourbon pepper, Nutmeg

Base Note -Cedarwood, Vetiver

Master perfumer- Olivier Cresp (Firmenich)
Features
 Olfactory Family - Woody floral
Top Notes - Bergamot, Violet leaves; Heart Notes - Violet flower, Bourbon pepper, Nutmeg; Base Notes - Cedarwood, Vetiver

After the success of the original and futurist Mercedes-Benz Club, and without denying its fundamental values of excellence and luxury, Mercedes-Benz Parfums wanted to go even more further, even more higher... This time with a unique concept of exclusive cooperation with the most talented Firmenich Master Perfumers. A collection of exclusive sensations that light up the night like a thousand sparkling stars.

Design- The slender silhouette of the Mercedes-Benz Club is unmistakable. Its pure, clean aesthetic. Its innovative spirit. And now its transformation into glass and color. Like urban architecture, a skyline lit up against the darkness of the night. The impressive, glossy, metallic cap echoes the instantly recognizable star set in the glass, while the silver signature of the Master Perfumer authenticates his or her composition.

Olfactive Family- Aromatic watery

Top Note- Blackcurrant, Bergamot

Heart Note- Ivy leaves, Galbanum

Base Note- Sandlewood, Tonka beans

Design- Revealing a soft pink juice, the bottle adds a bright, glamorous touch to every woman’s fragrance wardrobe. The bottle’s now famous curves are wrapped in gradated pink luminous, modern and trendy, catching the eye and attracting the hand. The iconic star signs the creation on top of the luxurious, glossy metal cap. The box follows suit, daring bright, remarkable, unforgettable rose pink, completed by the silver gravure that adds the fi nal, prestigious touch of excellence.

An enchanting, luxurious, unexpected fragrance created to accentuate and exalt a woman’s personality. A superb story of femininity and self-assurance, cloaking her in a fragrant aura of delicateness. Mercedes-Benz Woman is a rare, gourmand fragrance composed by a woman— acclaimed master perfumer Honorine Blanc—for women. A woman who knows and understands women, who recognizes and acknowledges their desires with intuition and savoir-faire.

Design- Sensual curves compose this monobloc flacon designed with the precision and exacting eye of a contemporary object. Sophisticated design for an inspired sculpture. At the heart of the pearlescent, velvety bottle, the transparency of glass embraces the legendary star. Purity and transparency, strength and delicacy, finesse and femininity, simplicity and perfection—a perfume, an original design, a pure object of desire.

Top Note- Brazilian gardenia, Pear

Heart Note- Jasmine sambac

Base Note- Vanilla, Musk

Master perfumer- Honorine Blanc
Features

The exceptional expertise of a master perfumer reveals this great timeless classic in a new light. A gentle breath of peaceful energy and a surge of sophisticated elegance promises the exceptional every day for a man who appreciates simplicity when it’s exclusive, the obvious when it’s inimitable.

Design- The peaceful harmony of turquoise and brushed metal unites with transparency to reveal the quiet confidence of contrast. The massive elegance and pure, distinct lines of the brand’s emblematic bottle are subtly reinvented in a perfect gradation of turquoise that recalls the line of the horizon. Ethereal, bright and luminous, like the pure, crystal-clear morning it evokes. Stamped with the legendary star, the silver cap is accentuated by dual white lines that emphasize the pure, light, fresh character of the design and fragrance. Strengthening its impact, the box is enhanced by metallic gleam, and the embossed star embodies the exclusivity of belonging.

Top Note- Grapefruit

Heart Note- Ginger, Verbena

Base Note- Vetiver, Musk

Master perfumer- Olivier Cresp (Firmenich)
Features

Are You Ready for a Night in the Town? Neon lights, vivid colours, edgy locations. Breathe in the energy of a bustling, lively city. Embrace the feeling of being young and free. Meet your party. Share your excitement. Live the moment. Join the movement. The night is yours. Enter into the music. Take your part of the fun, take your place in the Club. It’s time for Mercedes-Benz Club, a perfume for the new generation.

Design- The Bottle: Streamlined and futurist. Unique and original. Powerful and energetic. Young and modern. An aerodynamic shape that suggests speed and motion. A metal sculpture, like an architectured carapace, whose curves and lines reveal the coloured gleam of glass. An exceptional object containing even more exceptional than itself, engraved with the emblematic star.

Concept- The fragrance which oscillates between the fusing effect of the citrus coctail and the addictive sensuality elegant wood sillage. Made for the young and free man who believes in living in the moment.

Mercedes-Benz Man: the iconic perfume of an emblematic name is here. A perfume designed as the symbol of a lifestyle and a certain idea of success.
The authentic manifestation of the values of a mythical brand — this is the Mercedes-Benz legend in a bottle. Powerful personality, timeless elegance and a bold, understated attitude — his strong, self-assured character marks his presence. A perfume like a masterstroke dedicated to all who keep the Star, like a stimulating presence, in their sights.

Design- This splendid, high-tech bottle is the perfect transcription of the brand’s fundamentals. The mastery of glass and metal clad in soft-touch matte black. A spare silhouette with superb, shapely shoulders and a promise in its heart. The pure chrome lines of the emblematic Star, set in a halo of massive glass, stand out against the deep blue ground. Accomplished design and meticulous perfection for an exacting yet understated bottle. Bold and innovative, luxurious and discreet, resolutely masculine, contemporary... and different. Heat- embossed with the silver Star, the box echoes the graphic codes of the bottle it protects.

Top Note- Oak moss, Palisander

Heart Note- Geranium, Cedar leaf

Base Note -Ambrette seeds, Pear

Master perfumer- Olivier Cresp (Firmenich)

This is a sophisticated scent with a deep sillage that confirms the man’s identity and accentuates his singularity. A fragrance that goes beyond and challenges 
the limits of power and seduction. To last. A fragrance which is a concentrate of intensity and a true sublimation of the original fragrance.

Design- The perfume is enrobed in a black bottle. As black as night, as black as the intensity of a superb encounter. The infinitely masculine elegance of the gradated, lacquered glass reveals the perfume. Luxurious and contemporary. The Mercedes-Benz emblem, the famous three-pointed star, is engraved in relief in the bottom of the bottle. And like a seal on its elegant bonnet. The bottle nestles in a deep, matte, darkly luminous pack stamped with the silver star.

column35:
The first impression created by Jaguar Pace is of a stimulating trio of strong black pepper, fresh green apples and aromatic rosemary. The heady fragrance compound Cashmeran is what comes to the fore next. This raw material is the most important ingredient because it is very complex in character; a woody amber element with a spicy, almost peppery, fresh head note. The heart note is rounded off with aromatic lavender and luxurious orris, which marry elegantly with the classic, woody aromas of the base notes which include amberwood, patchouli and crystal moss. The overall fragrance experience creates a deep feeling of well-being that we can never tire of.
Features
 Olfactory Family - Aromatic-Fougères
Top Notes - Black Pepper, Green Apple, Rosemary; Heart Notes - Lavender, Cashmeran, Orris; Base Notes - Patchouli,Amberwood,Crystal Mos

FOUGÈRE, AROMATIC, WOODY, AMBER. The fragrance opens on penetrating head notes, based on a transparent and aquatic accord. These notes are reinforced with a touch of bergamot from Calabria and by the aromatic and persistent notes of ivy leaves. This enlarged freshness gives to this masculine jus a truly provocative effect. The contrasts appear in the heart note with a mystical and elegant note, expressed through the poudré touches of iris and white cedar, in turn emphasised by a seductive sage accord. Noble raw materials enrich and complete the sillage: a refined Cashmere wood mixture, with crystals of vegetable mosses, and a “skin” accord, which is the product of the soft musk.
Features
 Olfactory Family - Woody Aromatic
Top Notes - Calabrian Bergamot, Ivy Leaves, Aquatic Accord; Heart Notes - Clary Sage,Orris, White Cedar; Base Notes - Cashmere, Crystal Moss, Skin Musk

column8: Pure Matte Eyeshadow-01 -Sand Dunes-2 g / 0.07 oz
column31: A finely -milled, silky -matte eyeshadow for shading lids, lining eyes, and defining brows -pig. They come in a range of pigment -rich colors. column33:
Apply a light or medium -colored eye shadow all over the eyelid with an all over shadow brush.
Use a rounded crease brush to apply a darker shade to the outer corner of the eye. 
Blend the contours of the eyes with a clean brush to create a seamless look. 
Apply an eye shadow base of the same color before applying shadow for optimal wear.

column31: A powerfully pigmented eyeshadow refill with intense color payoff. This Single Eyeshadow Refill has a powerfully -pigmented formula that glides onto lids—delivering intense payoff with an ultra -luxe, powder -to -silk feel. And with finishes ranging from plush matte to shimmering metallic to sparkle and duo -chrome, each shade offers eye -catching possibilities.
column33:
Using a flat brush, apply a light shade across the eyelid, up to the crease. 
Using a smudging brush, apply a dark shade to the outer corner of the eye, and slightly blend inward. 
Use a medium shade to blend the edges of the dark shade into the light shade using a flat brush.

column8: Lip Palette X6  - 01  - Pink-01 -Pink-2 g / 0.07 oz (6X)
column31: Indulge in a tempting range of shades—from brazen berries to smoldering neutrals. This versatile lipstick palette will take you from day to date.  Bold, ultra -saturated color feels hydrating and stays put—it does not bleed or feather.
column33: Apply any of the shades straight from the pan, with your fingers or a lip brush. Use them alone, or blend them together for a wide range of possibilities. Apply the lightest shade to the lips as a base. Intensify the natural color of the lips by applying the medium shade. Create an ombré effect by applying a darker shade to the outer contours of the lips, then adding a lighter shade to the center, creating the illusion of additional volume.
